3. cs.LG (Machine Learning) - The proposed algorithm uses deep neural networks for implementation, which falls under the domain of machine learning. 
4. cs.RO (Robotics) - The paper discusses the planning problem for decentralized POMDPs, which is a common problem in robotics.
